y'=mu'e^{mu}=mu'y.
u'=\frac{1}{\sinh u}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{\cosh^2 u-1}}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{x^2-1}}.
y'=mu'y=\frac{my}{\sqrt{x^2-1}},\quad\text{and therefore}\quad \sqrt{x^2-1}\,y'=my.
y''\sqrt{x^2-1}+\frac{xy'}{\sqrt{x^2-1}}=my'.
(x^2-1)y'' +xy' =my'\sqrt{x^2-1}.
